## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2ec69-113">使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 属性可以指定 SOAP 正文元素中数据成员的位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ec69-113">Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property to specify the location of a data member in the SOAP body element.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ec69-114">该值不需要是连续的，因为它不表示成员的位置，只表示排序键。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ec69-114">The value is not required to be consecutive, because it does not represent the position of the member, only the sorting key.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2ec69-115">正文元素的默认顺序是按字母顺序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ec69-115">The order of the body elements is alphabetical by default.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ec69-116">此属性和 <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 属性的语义相同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ec69-116">The semantics of this property are the same as the semantics of the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2ec69-117">下面的代码示例使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 属性来首先序列化 `sourceAccount` 值，其次是 `targetAccount` 值，最后是 `amount` 值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ec69-117">The following code example uses the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property to serialize the `sourceAccount` value first, the `targetAccount` value second and the `amount` value third.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2ec69-118">如果不使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 属性，则会先序列化 `amount` 值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2ec69-118">If the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property is not used, the `amount` value is serialized first.</span></span>  
  
```  
[MessageContract]  
public class BankingTransaction  
{  
  [MessageHeader] public Operation operation;  
  [MessageBodyMember(Order=1)] public Account sourceAccount;  
  [MessageBodyMember(Order=2)] public Account targetAccount;  
  [MessageBodyMember(Order=3)] public int amount;  
}  
```
